# PR #11055: PS-70018 POM updates for Drawing detail overlay. Validating UDF field and empty Sharing Log.
**Tipo:** unknown
**Branch:** `wip/Justine/SharingHistory/PS-70018` → `sigma6/SharingHistory`

## Descripción
Updates `UserCanEditCustomFieldsInDrawingPropertiesPanel` browser test to use the detail overlay instead of the info panel for additional info fields. It also adds a basic sharing log visibility check.


